The base converter project helps you convert different numbers in different bases to other bases
The following are the base conversions offered
1- Binary number to Decimal
2- Decimal number to Binary
3- Binary number to Octal
4- Octal number to Binary
5- Decimal number to Octal
6- Octal number to Decimal

It makes use of six different functions for the respective operations mentioned.

It offers a do while loop to repeat the program in case of multiple conversions.

The codes may be a bit technical or confusing but try following each step.
NOTE: The modulo operations simply help with the remainders needed for conversion.
That makes it very understandable.
